Ok, im not sure how to do this but i will write here the changes i made to my Tab Menu 7 saved extension, which still works on load unpacked. It shows some errors but doesnt affect functionality.

To see a preview go here: https://i.imgur.com/yZxBL9g.png

1. I added placeholder="Search tabs" to 
    <body>
      <div id="main"><input id="search" spellcheck="false" placeholder="Search tabs" /></div>
    </body>
    
    
2. I stylized the css to better suit a dark environment and larger screens. I will paste here all the css, since im not sore what i changed and what not, and i see you also did some changes since v7.

// here goes the code: //

div, img {
  -webkit-user-select: none;
}

